flowchart TD
    Start([Start]) --> Operation{Choose Operation}
    
    Operation -->|Enqueue| CheckFull{Is Queue Full?}
    Operation -->|Dequeue| CheckEmpty1{Is Queue Empty?}
    Operation -->|Peek| CheckEmpty2{Is Queue Empty?}
    
    %% Enqueue Flow
    CheckFull -->|Yes| OverflowError[Return Error:<br/>Queue Overflow]
    CheckFull -->|No| AddElement[Add element to rear]
    AddElement --> UpdateRear[Update rear pointer]
    UpdateRear --> IncrementSize[Increment size]
    IncrementSize --> Success1[Return Success]
    
    %% Dequeue Flow
    CheckEmpty1 -->|Yes| UnderflowError[Return Error:<br/>Queue Underflow]
    CheckEmpty1 -->|No| SaveValue[Save front element value]
    SaveValue --> RemoveFront[Remove front element]
    RemoveFront --> UpdateFront[Update front pointer]
    UpdateFront --> DecrementSize[Decrement size]
    DecrementSize --> ReturnValue[Return saved value]
    
    %% Peek Flow
    CheckEmpty2 -->|Yes| EmptyError[Return Error:<br/>Queue is Empty]
    CheckEmpty2 -->|No| ReturnFront[Return front element<br/>without removing]
    
    OverflowError --> End([End])
    Success1 --> End
    UnderflowError --> End
    ReturnValue --> End
    EmptyError --> End
    ReturnFront --> End
    
    style Start fill:#90EE90
    style End fill:#FFB6C1
    style OverflowError fill:#FF6B6B
    style UnderflowError fill:#FF6B6B
    style EmptyError fill:#FF6B6B
    style Success1 fill:#4ECDC4
    style ReturnValue fill:#4ECDC4
    style ReturnFront fill:#4ECDC4